* Iron Raptor kept her eyes on Cheetor for a moment before her attention was 
grabbed by a transmission by Hysteria, sighing in reliefe and scanning that 
the Alliance prisiners had escaped the shop and awaited for the shields to 
be dropped.
It wasn't easy to give a command where it would leave the ship without 
defences, though there might be a way around it.*

" Cat't you just drop off a section so that they can get out? Leaving the 
rest of the shields up?"

* She spoke this and then waited, glancing at Cheetor again but was eased 
when he decided just to lay back and stay in line with everyone else.
But then Iron Raptor looked towards another voice, seeing that it was 
Rhinox. It was strange sometimes how people asked for orders or commands, 
like they want to be sent out to go and do something. Must be bord then.
She shook her head.*

" There are none to give out other then maintaining the cease fire and 
watching the Alliance."

* There was no telling just what the Alliance could do now and if they would 
leave once the captives had been released. But she hoped that they were just 
as tired of this battle as she was and ready to go back to their own base 
that needed it's own protecting.
But then Iron Raptor suddenly remembered something, feeling rather guilty 
for forgetting.
There was still the small kitten in her back compartment!
She reached back to get hold of him, trying to get a punch of neck fur 
between her fingers to pull him out. But it wasn't long before there was 
some other sound which attracted her attention while she was trying to get 
the cat. It was a musical voice, and it was greeted by her with a slightly 
annoyed sigh.
It was one thing after another.
< Could you reply to that, Prowl?>*
